snippet.title: The Signal From Tölva - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
The Signal From Tölva is a single-player first-person exploration and combat game from UK developer Big Robot. Available for Windows and OSX in early 2017. 
http://www.thesignalfrom.com/
